    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Scions descended from armor-plated celestials or anarchic warrior entities have an affinity for armor—it fits perfectly and protects more efficiently, as though it were an extension of the scion themself. When wearing armor, they gain a +1 species bonus to AC. When they’re wearing heavy armor, their armor check penalty is 1 less severe than normal.</p>\n<p><strong>This replaces celestial radiance for aasimars or reverse fate for ganzis.</strong></p>\n<p><strong></strong></p><strong></strong><p><strong></strong><em>Enable/Disable modifiers in the Modifiers tab.</em></p>"
